name: Cyrce's Circlet
description: Sea dogs and tale spinners tell stories of a mythical siren that could lure even the stubbornest sailors to a watery grave.

spells.description: Equip: You are one of the devout. Your spells and abilities have a chance of burning a nearby enemy for 372,739 Radiant damage and healing another devout ally for that amount.

Use: Draw out a piece of the target's soul, decreasing their movement speed by 30% until the soul reaches you. The soul instantly heals you for 430,331, and grants you up to 9,985 Critical Strike for 16 sec. You gain more Critical Strike from lower health targets. (2 Min Cooldown)
